StrategyRuntimeInstance: MISSING

Confirmed absent from all code. AdmissionTrialBinding is implicitly carrying runtime responsibilities (campaign_id, runtime_carrier_id, status progression through 8+ states) but was designed as a planning/binding fact. BoundedRiskCampaign is a risk-budget container, not a strategy runtime identity. A first-class StrategyRuntimeInstance is needed to separate planning from execution and provide a stable identity for the signal→intent→order→review chain.

